<td class="mbox-text" style="">It has been suggested that this section be <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Splitting" title="Wikipedia:Splitting">split</a> into a new article. (<a href="/wiki/Talk:Teletext" title="Talk:Teletext">Discuss</a>)</td>
